      <title>Brookfield 即将达成协议收购 Neoen 多数股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/brookfield-nears-deal-to-buy-majority-stake-in-neoen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Brookfield 即将收购 Neoen SA 53% 的股份，这笔交易对这家法国可再生能源开发商的估值约为 61 亿欧元（66 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/brookfield-nears-deal-to-buy-majority-stake-in-neoen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛将印度股票、债券和卢比视为新兴市场的首选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/goldman-sees-india-s-stocks-bonds-and-rupee-among-top-em-picks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，得益于充满活力的经济和保护印度免受全球市场影响的政策，印度的股票、债券和货币是新兴市场中最具吸引力的投资对象之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/goldman-sees-india-s-stocks-bonds-and-rupee-among-top-em-picks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 02:53:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
